17fab922-e2c0-4b7e-9b27-e1d39acdf042	Title: McCall MacBain Scholarship 2027\nCountry: Canada\nDegree level: masters\nFunding type: full\nDeadline: 19 August 2026\nOfficial URL: https://apply.mccallmacbainscholars.org/\n\nDescription:\nThe McCall MacBain Scholarship is a prestigious, leadership-based full scholarship for master's studies at McGill University in Montreal, Canada. It covers full tuition and mandatory fees, provides a monthly living stipend of CAD 2,300 (approximately BDT 2.0–2.1 lakh), and includes a relocation grant for moving to Montreal. Up to 30 full scholarships and 100 entrance awards are offered annually to candidates from all countries. Eligibility: current students completing a first bachelor's degree by August 2027, graduates within the last five years (since January 2021), or those who earned their degree earlier and were 30 or younger on 1 January 2026. International applicants (outside Canada and the US)	{"index": 0, "title": "McCall MacBain Scholarship 2027", "country": "Canada"}	[-0.006752014,-0.000117361546,0.052490234,-0.024475098,0.020141602,0.044311523,-0.03439331,-0.036865234,-0.0005722046,-0.033111572,0.015068054,0.027908325,-0.0016403198,0.022125244,0.0046806335,0.018936157,0.033996582,-0.018615723,-0.042266846,0.045043945,0.028121948,-0.0043029785,0.030700684,0.030685425,-0.017623901,-0.030319214,-0.011390686,-0.009140015,-0.03765869,0.017440796,0.008911133,0.0014944077,0.049041748,-0.024993896,-0.018707275,0.024856567,-0.042022705,0.024230957,0.041137695,0.03378296,-0.010101318,-0.032928467,0.08618164,0.043060303,-0.015213013,0.020355225,0.02558899,0.019989014,0.0014839172,-0.026153564,0.040618896,0.03152466,0.03994751,-0.024490356,-0.06768799,-0.037353516,0.039154053,-0.009796143,0.014762878,0.032318115,0.020706177,0.012367249,0.012863159,-0.027008057,-0.037109375,0.00040578842,-0.009994507,0.04095459,0.035064697,0.040649414,0.0063476562,0.010818481,0.0055389404,0.011482239,0.06021118,-0.033843994,0.009933472,0.006374359,0.0013