8194de4d-5352-44cf-93b3-7b18e304fa0a	or students pursuing English-taught degrees in technology and innovation.\n\nFor students from countries like Bangladesh, this is an excellent opportunity to gain an international degree in a tech-forward Baltic hub, combining affordable living costs with a prestigious academic environment.\n\nEligibility:\nOpen to international students, including those from South Asia, applying for Bachelor's or Master's degrees. Eligibility is based on academic merit and admission to English-taught programs at KTU.\n\nTips:\n• Highlight academic achievements and high GPA in your application documents.\n• Write a strong motivation letter explaining why Lithuania and KTU are ideal for your career goals.\n• Ensure all transcripts are officially translated and certified.\n• Apply early to secure your spot and scholarship consideration before the June deadline.\n\nTags: Lithuania, Europe, Partial Funding, Merit-based,	{"index": 1, "title": "Kaunas University of Technology Scholarship 2026 Scholarship", "country": "Lithuania"}	[0.0146865845,-0.064453125,-0.045532227,0.0011358261,0.024139404,0.032958984,0.004261017,-0.029922485,0.02418518,-0.0368042,0.050048828,-0.0011100769,-0.013465881,0.0022830963,-0.024993896,0.025756836,0.010536194,-0.050048828,-0.07543945,0.00466156,0.0066871643,-0.004547119,0.015472412,0.050872803,-0.016036987,0.015823364,-0.033843994,-0.011459351,-0.0006380081,-0.0037250519,0.04940796,0.011199951,0.0099487305,-0.010002136,0.015594482,-0.020095825,-0.00680542,0.01713562,-6.1929226e-05,0.010902405,-0.02810669,0.021392822,0.0050621033,0.008918762,0.068237305,0.049804688,0.027038574,0.005268097,0.0052871704,-0.028762817,-0.05392456,0.07470703,0.04824829,0.024520874,-0.058746338,0.0015897751,0.032318115,-0.0017156601,-0.025970459,0.0309906,0.088134766,-0.019577026,0.03189087,0.0005054474,-0.019256592,0.018463135,0.0287323,0.029067993,-0.0037460327,0.023452759,0.024780273,0.001572609,0.0004184246,-0.041168213,0.030731201,-0.0523071