248c206b-0d32-4fc7-b3e9-493d72376af7	fits including full tuition, a monthly stipend of approximately 1,750 MAD, accommodation, medical insurance, and airfare support, this scholarship removes significant financial barriers. While most programs are taught in French, the inclusion of a one-year language preparation course makes this opportunity accessible even to those without prior French proficiency. For Bangladeshi students, the key challenge lies in securing nomination through official channels, making early engagement with the Ministry of Education or Moroccan Embassy absolutely critical to success.\n\nEligibility:\nBangladeshi students must be nominated by the Bangladesh Ministry of Education or Embassy to apply. Open to Bachelor's, Master's, and PhD candidates across all fields. Applicants typically need strong academic records and must be prepared to study in French, with a one-year language preparation course available	{"index": 1, "title": "Morocco Government Scholarship 2025/2026 (AMCI)", "country": "Morocco"}	[-0.06100464,-0.003780365,0.015808105,0.028915405,0.049224854,0.049438477,0.039093018,0.01134491,0.0005016327,-0.04196167,0.018661499,0.012382507,-0.035614014,-0.0034008026,0.006954193,0.002231598,0.03829956,-0.008216858,-0.013374329,0.002275467,0.04360962,0.030410767,0.018203735,0.038909912,0.009681702,0.013908386,-0.022735596,-0.0013904572,-0.021453857,0.03616333,-0.014762878,0.016738892,0.023864746,0.008850098,-0.015380859,0.022567749,-0.03152466,0.03366089,-0.0011148453,0.027313232,0.01586914,0.0046424866,0.005420685,-0.0140686035,0.01158905,0.038513184,0.03567505,-0.012199402,0.040161133,-0.009399414,-0.015625,0.08215332,0.031463623,-0.047790527,-0.06088257,-0.027053833,-0.0017728806,0.007789612,-0.008934021,0.027542114,0.023910522,-0.0052833557,0.053771973,0.02519226,0.006465912,0.04425049,-0.00015485287,0.032287598,0.03933716,0.03540039,0.009254456,0.0340271,0.002986908,0.04324341,0.045928955,-0.0061798096,-0.075683594,0.06439209,0.048309326,0.