d4e42209-c418-49b9-b127-516e583d494d	while PhD candidates require a relevant honors or masters degree with excellent grades. CGPA requirements vary by department but competitive applicants usually hold a minimum equivalent to a First Class or Upper Second Class degree.\n\nTips:\n• Apply early in the academic year to secure supervisor availability and funding allocation before quotas fill\n• Craft a compelling research proposal aligned with Otago's strategic research priorities and identified supervisor expertise\n• Secure a supervisor commitment before submitting your formal scholarship application\n• Highlight any published research, conference presentations, or relevant professional experience in your CV\n• Prepare strong reference letters from academic referees who can speak to your research capability and potential\n\nTags: New Zealand, University of Otago, Masters, PhD, Full Funding, Tuition Coverage, Stipend, Research Support	{"index": 2, "title": "University of Otago Scholarships 2026-27", "country": "New Zealand"}	[-0.0020103455,-0.017318726,0.02897644,0.0007109642,0.002632141,0.027938843,-0.010475159,-0.028244019,0.008049011,-0.007499695,0.030517578,-0.01411438,0.04537964,-0.019592285,-0.00932312,0.00497818,0.01586914,-0.024017334,0.00573349,0.03286743,-0.021621704,0.013046265,0.026809692,0.07476807,0.043029785,0.014633179,-0.0446167,0.060821533,-0.02444458,-0.022949219,0.02709961,0.024124146,0.012565613,-0.0143585205,0.02822876,0.026489258,0.012062073,-0.032409668,0.0104904175,0.016525269,-0.005722046,0.055877686,0.028503418,0.018157959,0.02557373,0.00667572,-0.03289795,-0.00011128187,0.0062675476,0.0066223145,-0.0059661865,0.055664062,0.030578613,0.010986328,-0.051635742,-0.06060791,0.048614502,-0.02973938,-0.03250122,0.04058838,0.038482666,-0.031143188,-0.0020160675,-0.047424316,0.021774292,0.034820557,0.024353027,0.018707275,0.005744934,-0.017532349,0.011810303,0.009048462,-0.050476074,0.01158905,0.02218628,-0.011764526,-0.03640747,0.018035889,-0.004680