8d72c3d4-9da2-4827-bda7-f2bbff174c71	and a clear vision to contribute to Bangladesh's development. With a highly competitive selection process, successful applicants often have a well-defined research proposal that addresses key challenges like climate resilience, healthcare, or education. This scholarship not only offers world-class education but also connects you to a global network of leaders committed to positive change.\n\nEligibility:\nOpen to citizens of Commonwealth countries (including Bangladesh) applying for Master's or PhD degrees in the UK. Requires a strong academic record (typically a first-class or upper second-class degree) and a clear development impact plan for your home country. No age limit, but priority is given to those who have not previously studied in the UK.\n\nTips:\n• Align your research proposal or study plan with the development needs of Bangladesh (e.g., climate change, public health, education).\n•	{"index": 1, "title": "Commonwealth Scholarship", "country": "United Kingdom"}	[-0.032470703,-0.051940918,-0.02180481,0.027816772,0.020706177,0.015304565,-0.02243042,-0.008277893,0.037353516,-0.08026123,-0.0032157898,-0.023025513,-0.0211792,-0.038269043,-0.0011472702,0.017608643,0.062164307,-0.0059890747,-0.031555176,0.017059326,0.031036377,-0.01171875,0.07409668,0.041656494,0.0062561035,0.014266968,-0.021408081,0.01977539,-0.043914795,0.014282227,0.02734375,0.026931763,0.024307251,0.0066833496,0.037963867,-0.023086548,-0.026931763,-0.041870117,-0.007423401,-0.00049591064,0.019989014,0.016555786,0.045776367,0.03125,0.019180298,0.054138184,0.027053833,-0.0036029816,0.0051994324,0.003967285,-0.04260254,0.03970337,0.024749756,0.017288208,-0.06072998,-0.0061569214,-0.0017089844,-0.015716553,-0.032470703,0.045013428,0.036010742,0.012123108,0.018310547,-0.031341553,-0.014297485,0.008430481,0.037109375,0.017349243,-0.0018558502,0.012145996,-0.009208679,0.022003174,-0.002073288,0.014297485,0.019226074,-0.025344849,-0.06939697,0.010986328,0.0312042