0f263032-1412-44f5-8e2c-e6912f402f0e	Title: University of Verona PhD Scholarships 2026-27 in Italy\nCountry: Italy\nDegree level: phd\nFunding type: full\nDeadline: 9 June 2026\nOfficial URL: https://www.univr.it/en/our-services/phd-programmes\n\nDescription:\nThe University of Verona offers fully funded PhD scholarships for the 2026-27 academic year. The scholarship covers an annual stipend of €17,602, a €250 registration fee waiver, and provides access to advanced research facilities and international collaboration opportunities across Europe. A total of 104 PhD scholarships are available. Applicants can apply to up to three PhD programmes, each requiring a separate €10 application fee. Eligibility: open to international students; applicants must hold a Master's degree (MA/MSc or equivalent); IELTS is not mandatory but proof of English proficiency may be required depending on the programme. The deadline for applications is 9 June	{"index": 0, "title": "University of Verona PhD Scholarships 2026-27 in Italy", "country": "Italy"}	[-0.0053253174,-0.056884766,0.06298828,-0.024932861,-0.007381439,0.017913818,-0.01348114,0.002439499,-0.020645142,-0.078063965,0.04434204,-0.057800293,-0.035247803,-0.032440186,0.006679535,0.017410278,0.04550171,-0.012306213,-0.010192871,-0.0009813309,-0.0057907104,0.022857666,0.0007343292,0.041015625,-0.019561768,-0.012161255,-0.02255249,0.036376953,-0.08728027,0.04345703,0.051116943,-0.002696991,0.010055542,-0.026809692,-0.021331787,-0.004272461,0.013290405,0.0010938644,-0.0054092407,-0.02645874,-0.025360107,0.007160187,-0.0033893585,0.0335083,0.033111572,0.0362854,0.042816162,0.0060424805,0.031921387,0.015945435,-0.017944336,0.029159546,0.011619568,-0.011039734,-0.028900146,-0.03717041,-0.0012493134,0.020935059,-0.029815674,-0.0018014908,0.05722046,-0.019119263,0.04486084,-0.019348145,-0.02418518,0.031585693,0.009521484,0.03793335,-0.017211914,0.018707275,0.009864807,0.00076007843,-0.03378296,-0.006515503,-0.0002682209,0.010772705,-0.017