7ddfa98e-1ca4-4594-841f-c07c953ae271	Title: Aarhus University Danish State Scholarship 2026\nCountry: Denmark\nDegree level: masters\nFunding type: partial\nDeadline: 15 September 2026\nOfficial URL: https://masters.au.dk/scholarships-and-grants\n\nDescription:\nAarhus University offers a limited number of Danish state scholarships for non-EU/EEA students applying to Master's degree programmes. The scholarship is awarded automatically to talented applicants based on academic merit; no separate application is needed. Coverage varies by faculty: some faculties offer a full tuition fee waiver, while others include a monthly living grant in addition to the tuition waiver. The scholarship is not available to EU/EEA/Swiss students. Applicants must meet the admission requirements, including English proficiency (e.g., IELTS Academic 6.5 minimum). The application deadline for winter admission (starting in February) is 15 September 2026; for	{"index": 0, "title": "Aarhus University Danish State Scholarship 2026", "country": "Denmark"}	[-0.030838013,-0.037872314,0.010719299,-0.027114868,0.007194519,0.011360168,-0.044525146,-0.053741455,-0.04159546,-0.050201416,0.066345215,-0.0413208,-0.0010843277,-0.0021514893,-0.006504059,0.002872467,0.06225586,-0.005554199,-0.018005371,-0.019317627,-0.00015032291,-0.03744507,-0.04876709,0.019714355,-0.001953125,-0.021011353,0.023361206,0.061706543,-0.054901123,0.011207581,0.008392334,0.007858276,-0.010192871,-0.02142334,-0.0013399124,0.0038261414,-0.0009622574,0.026687622,0.025665283,0.049041748,-0.030395508,0.0012693405,0.034179688,0.07098389,0.0030822754,0.039367676,0.08013916,0.009460449,0.017333984,-0.00182724,0.0026607513,0.015419006,0.014587402,-0.007587433,-0.01991272,-0.012359619,0.032318115,0.018081665,-0.0146102905,0.04840088,0.08691406,0.04083252,0.047058105,-0.03665161,-0.00932312,0.02696228,0.026428223,0.037994385,-0.0075569153,0.049804688,0.014167786,0.010047913,-0.0017051697,-0.022720337,0.04827881,-0.028625488,-0.006641388,-0