1fba9f88-ee47-49d4-9b96-6f510e8a107d	art of Wellington.\n\nEligibility:\nOpen to outstanding international students applying for Bachelor's, Master's, or PhD programs at Victoria University of Wellington. Applicants must demonstrate strong academic records and meet the university's entry requirements. No specific CGPA or nationality restrictions are mentioned, but competitiveness is high.\n\nTips:\n• Start your application early to gather all required documents and meet the July 2026 deadline.\n• Showcase exceptional academic achievements, research experience, and extracurricular activities in your statement.\n• Secure strong letters of recommendation from professors or employers who can attest to your abilities.\n• Ensure your English proficiency scores (IELTS/TOEFL) meet VUW's requirements.\n• Carefully review the scholarship terms and conditions on the official website before applying.\n\nTags: New Zealand, full scholarship, interna	{"index": 2, "title": "VUW International Scholarship", "country": "New Zealand"}	[0.00019609928,-0.072509766,-0.015357971,0.020935059,0.033966064,0.033111572,-0.03866577,0.014083862,-0.009140015,-0.058288574,0.076171875,0.006164551,0.038116455,0.019500732,-0.025817871,0.0021591187,0.021026611,-0.01864624,-0.037841797,0.0034999847,-0.0024967194,-0.01864624,0.010368347,0.077819824,0.03060913,-0.007850647,-0.0050468445,0.013839722,-0.018722534,0.031707764,-0.0012922287,0.009811401,-0.014167786,0.015449524,0.016357422,0.031402588,0.016555786,0.025405884,0.028625488,-0.025299072,0.008010864,0.020751953,0.014305115,0.025634766,0.009384155,0.014091492,0.022506714,-0.02583313,-0.02267456,-0.013282776,-0.0039749146,0.032226562,0.03579712,-0.0005431175,0.022659302,-0.041015625,0.02949524,0.013305664,0.011482239,0.016677856,0.008666992,-0.008682251,-0.032470703,0.013504028,-0.028945923,0.041168213,0.0039711,0.03677368,0.007167816,0.018188477,-0.015205383,-0.0024471283,-0.053985596,-0.06222534,0.054382324,0.023788452,-0.04537964,0.0014753342,-0.0