, mathematical finance or theoretical physics). Do a summer research project, online course from Coursera/edX, or write a paper\n5. **Create impact** – Start a math/physics tutoring club for underprivileged students, or a science magazine at your school\n6. **Get strong recommendation letters**	0	2026-06-10 18:12:17.648098+00	\N	2026-06-11 18:12:16.673+00
