n leadership experience** (even small projects count).\n- **Draft a powerful vision statement** about fintech and Bangladesh.\n\n**Deadline:** 11 October 2026. You have time—start preparing now.	0	2026-06-12 16:49:09.336924+00	\N	2026-06-13 16:49:09.244+00
